## 🛠️ Tech Stack

- **Microsoft Power BI** — Dashboard & visualization
- **Power Query** — Data transformation & cleaning
- **DAX** — Calculated measures & KPIs
- **Data Modeling** — Relationships & schema design

---

## 📊 Key Features

- ✅ Interactive **filters & slicers** for dynamic analysis
- ✅ **KPI cards** showing key business metrics
- ✅ **Charts & graphs** for trend analysis
- ✅ **Drill-through** capability for detailed insights
- ✅ **Mobile responsive** layout
- ✅ Real-time **data refresh** support

---

## 🏗️ Dashboard Components

| Component | Description |
|-----------|-------------|
| **KPI Cards** | High-level summary metrics |
| **Bar/Column Charts** | Category-wise comparisons |
| **Line Charts** | Trend analysis over time |
| **Slicers** | Interactive data filtering |
| **Tables** | Detailed data view |

